link:labelLink.link:label: Party Demographics
Organisation Details ATM Service Points Count
This is the number, as at the relevant date, of Automatic Teller Machines (ATM) service points.
Organisation Details EFTPOS Service Points Count
This is the number, as at the relevant date, of Electronic Funds Transfer at Point of Sale (EFTPOS) service points.
Organisation Details Minimum Branch Requirement Indicator
This indicates whether, as at the relevant date, the service channel has satisfied the Australian Prudential Regulation Authority's minimum branch requirement.
Party Entity Relationship Group Code
A code which identifies a group of entity relationship types.
Valid values are: CONSOLIDATION-GROUPING = Consolidation and Grouping Relationships ASSOCIATES = Associates Relationships
Party Entity Relationship Type Code
A code which identifies the relationship from one entity to another entity.

Valid values are: PTNRSHP-PTNR = Partnership to Partner PTNR-PTNRSHP = Partner to Partnership LTDPTNRSHP-PTNR = Limited Partnership to Partner PTNR-LTDPTNRSHP = Partner to Limited Partnership CMP-DTR = Company to Director DTR-CMP = Director to Company CMP-PBLOFFCR = Company to Public Officer PBLOFFCR-CMP = Public Officer to Company CMP-OFFCBRR = Company to Office Bearer OFFCBRR-CMP = Office Bearer to Company CMP-TRSTEE = Company to Trustee TRSTEE-CMP = Trustee to Company TRST-TRSTEE = Trust to Trustee TRSTEE-TRST = Trustee to Trust SF-TRSTEE = Superannuation Fund to Trustee TRSTEE-SF = Trustee to Superannuation Fund SF-TRSTEEDTR = Superannuation Fund to Trustee Director TRSTEEDTR-SF = Trustee Director to Superannuation Fund SF-MBR = Superannuation Fund to Member MBR-SF = Member to Superannuation Fund ITGRPHD-ITGRPMBR = Income Tax Group Head to Income Tax Group Member ITGRPMBR-ITGRPHD = Income Tax Group Member to Income Tax Group Head NMTDHDCMP-ITGRPMBR = Nominated Head Company to Income Tax Group Member ITGRPMBR-NMTDHDCMP = Income Tax Group Member to Nominated Head Company GSTGRPREP-GRPMBR = GST Group Representative to Group Member GRPMBR-GSTGRPREP = GST Group Member to Group Representative GSTRELGRPPRNPL-MBR = GST Religious Group Principal to Member MBR-GSTRELGRPPRNPL = GST Religious Group Member to Principal
